<h1>Character Tiles</h1>

<p>Click on a tile to see its stats and any scenarios it appears in.</p>
  <p>Tiles can be sorted by:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>the box (<strong>origin</strong>) the tile came in</li>
        <li>the <strong>type</strong> of unit the tile represents</li>
        <li>by unit type for <strong>Versus</strong> recruitment</li>
        <li>tile <strong>name</strong> listed with their stats</li>
      </ul>
<div align="center">
  <a href="" id="show_byorigin" class="toggles"><button class="btn btn-tile active">By Origin</button></a>
  <a href="" id="show_bytype" class="toggles"><button class="btn btn-tile">By Type</button></a>
  <a href="" id="show_forversus" class="toggles"><button class="btn btn-tile">Versus</button></a>

  <a href="" id="show_bystat" class="toggles"><button class="btn btn-tile">Name / Stats</button></a>
</div>
<hr>
